{
  "stem": "27507.11",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But on Praga, in our part of Warsaw east of the Vistula, also there was an uprising, but that one was repressed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Germans managed to cause the surrender of the uprising after only a few days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they practically emptied all of this part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People had to leave their houses, and they were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And anyway, the Russians were coming quite close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think that by then, the Russian artillery could be already heard because they were coming quite close to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In August they were-- they were coming close, and then the Polish uprising started because the Polish command thought that the Russians were there any day, practically.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the Russians then stopped east of Warsaw and didn't progress any further, whether it was on purpose or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they then stood quite close to Warsaw for about a month, and they didn't even come all the way to the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we remained politically on the front line.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "For the next six weeks, maybe, we remained on the front line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there-- were-- it was, as well, our-- the Kopers, our lent householders, they were not there as well because they had to evacuate-- to get evacuated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they left probably in early August, and they went-- we knew where they went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They didn't go terribly far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They went to their little shed somewhere, about 15 or 20 kilometers from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we're left completely alone in this terrain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was not any authority anymore, except there was the army there, and the army was the soldiers, so we were spending most of the time in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The soldiers were coming occasionally.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
